reviewText: These girls are funny, funny, funny, great chemistry between them. For stupid fun pop one of these DVDs in and stand back.
Forget all your troubles and just laugh your head off!
Quality of the videos exceeded my expectations!
i love the simple life!! it's hilarious and u can watch it when you're bored! the qualities are good and it's not bad!
I bought this collection of shows for my roommate and I to watch in between study breaks. The DVDs all came wrapped in their original packaging and are hysterical to watch.
This video bring everyone back to the REAL LIFE that everyone should be at. No matter how much money you have someone does live like the Simple Life.

All of the seasons of Simple Life were good. Very funny show. Still the best reality show ever! Fans have their favorite seasons, but all of the seasons are good and worth watching! We love it!
Thanks,

arrived prior to expected date of delivery; a little excessive with the packaging..took me like 15 minutes to take all the wrapping off of the dvds..overall a good experience with this seller
